<h2>Confirm Your Email Address</h2>

<p>Hi {{userName}},</p>

<p>Thank you for registering at
  <strong>{{appName}}</strong>! To complete your registration and activate your account, please verify your email address by clicking the link below:</p>

<p class='link-text'>{{verifyUrl}}</p>

<div class='warning-box'>
  <p><strong>Important security information:</strong></p>
  <p>• For your security, this link will expire in <strong>{{expiresInMin}} minutes</strong>.</p>
</div>

<div class='divider'></div>

<p style='color: #999999; font-size: 14px;'>
  If you did not create an account, please ignore this email. If you have any concerns, contact us through our website:
  <a href='{{appUrl}}/contact' style='color: #667eea;'>{{appName}}</a>.
</p>